<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 Khrih kan Bawipa, Sui luchin chinh u, Dong hin loin thangthat ko u si;
 A min upat sunh-lawihnak um seh, Atu in zungzal tiang.

[C1]
   Chinhter u si, (Chinhter u si), Chinhter u si, (Chinhter u si),
   Sunparnak ram ah kan Siangpahrang, Chinhter, Chinhter u si, Thang-thatnak
   dong lo in.

[V2]
 Vanmi run nih sangin an thangthat, A bawithutdan hmaiah an thangthat;
 Miphun vialte zong nih thangthat u, Bawibik cu thangthat u.

[C2]
   Chinhter u si, (Chinhter u si), Chinhter u si, (Chinhter u si),
   Sunparnak ram ah kan Siangpahrang, Chinhter, Chinhter u si, Thang-thatnak
   dong lo in.

[V3]
 Sualnak vialte teitu Bawi a si, A Thlarau in kan lungthin peng seh.
 Amah min in teitu kan si lai, Zungzal in chinhter u.

[C3]
   Chinhter u si, (Chinhter u si), Chinhter u si, (Chinhter u si),
   Sunparnak ram ah kan Siangpahrang, Chinhter, Chinhter u si, Thang-thatnak
   dong lo in.</lyrics>
<key>G</key>
<title>SIANGPAHRANG LUCHIN CHINH U CH14</title>
<hymn_number>14</hymn_number>
</song>